liamentary) constituencies in [[Kerala]] state in southern [[India]].\n\n==Assembly segments==\n\nMalappuram Lok Sabha constituency is composed of the following assembly segments:\n{|class=\"wikitable\" width=\"500px\"  style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: 2px #666666 solid; font-size: x-big; font-family: API PHONETIQUE\"\n!width=\"50px\" style=\"font-size:75%\"|Constituency number\n!width=\"150px\" style=\"font-size:95%\"|Name\n!width=\"100px\" style=\"font-size:75%\"|Reserved for ([[Dalit|SC]]/[[Adivasi|ST]]/None)\n!width=\"150px\" style=\"font-size:95%\"|District\n|-\n|33\n|[[Kondotty (State Assembly constituency)|Kondotty]]\n|None\n|[[Malappuram district|Malappuram]]\n|-\n|37\n|[[Manjeri (State Assembly constituency)|Manjeri]]\n|None\n|[[Malappuram district|Malappuram]]\n|-\n|38\n|[[Perinthalmanna (State Assembly constituency)|Perinthalmanna]]\n|None\n|[[Malappuram district|Malappuram]]\n|-\n|39\n|[[Mankada (State Assembly constituency)|Mankada]]\n|None\n|[[Malappuram district|Malappuram]]\n|-\n|40\n|[[Malappuram (State Assembly constituency)|Malappuram]]\n|None\n|[[Malappuram district|Malappuram]]\n|-\n|41\n|[[Vengara (State Assembly constituency)|Vengara]]\n|None\n|[[Malappuram district|Malappuram]]\n|-\n|42\n|[[Vallikkunnu (State Assembly constituency)|Vallikkunnu]]\n|None\n|[[Malappuram district|Malappuram]]\n|-\n|}\n\n==Members of Parliament==\n\n'''Key'''\n\n{{Party index link|Indian Union Muslim League}}\n\n{| class=\"sortable\" width=\"50%\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border: 2px #000000 solid; font-size: x-big; font-family: API PHONETIQUE\"\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Election\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Lok Sabha\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Member\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" colspan=\"2\"|Party\n! style=\"background-color:#666666; color:white\" |Tenure\n|-\n\n| [[2009 Indian general election|2009]